value:
Hmph! Everyone 'round here seems
so damn anxious... Me? I'm great!

Lemme tell ya, back in Múspell, the
idea of swimming in some ocean
never even crossed my mind.

You call this heat? Pathetic. Múspell
winters are hotter than this.

Back in the filth pile I'm from, all
we had was a stinking swamp... This
big blue ocean is somethin' else.

That Ylgr brat is at the beach too?!
Come and play with me, she says...
Hrmph. We'll see about that.

Name's Helbindi. I hate doing stuff
like this, but I had to...this time. You
can thank $Nf.

Things are finally starting to get
interesting around here! Maybe the
beach ain't so bad after all!
Yeah! I'm gettin' fired up!
Huh? What the hell?! How pathetic.
Not bad! You got any more?

I'm Helbindi. Next to the dirt hole
I crawled out of, this beach is like
some kind of damn paradise.

When I was invited to the beach, the
idea itself pissed me off.$k$pBut I gotta admit, it turns out the
beach ain't half bad.$k$pLots of little brats running around,
having fun... If Menja were here, I bet
she'd be doing the same...$k$p...Ugh, never mind... And quit
looking at me like that, got it?$k$pAnyway, I guess I'll stick with you
if this is the kind of thing I'm in for.
So...where ya makin' me go next?
そらぁっ！
沈めやっ！
ぐああっ！
てめぇっ…！
Hotter'n Múspell!
Can't take the heat? Heh.
Last thing you'll look at.
Eat sand!
Dead in the water...
Now what?
Me? Been to the ocean before? You're funny.
Who do you think you're pushing?
Look at me in this damn swimsuit! Nuts to that.
You laughin' at me? I will end you.
You call this hot? I come from Múspell.
Maybe Menja'll show up. Maybe...
Hey, you! My sister... You could maybe... Ehhh, forget it.
Whatever.
You call this summer?
I'm gonna swim.
